query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_vials,
  brand,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN partNumber LIKE '%Vial%' OR partNumber LIKE '%vial%' THEN 1 END) as wrong_part_numbers
FROM products 
WHERE name LIKE '%vial%' OR name LIKE '%Vial%' OR productId LIKE '%Vial%'
GROUP BY brand
ORDER BY total_vials DESC;
